e: 20px">11:00<br /><span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 宋体;font-size: 20px;mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥;mso-ascii-font-family: ˎ̥">地点：攀枝花学院明德楼旁堆放处。</span><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 'ˎ̥','serif';font-size: 20px">
